}} The Town of 'Branch' is an incorporated community on the Cape Shore of
Newfoundland and Labrador, Canada and has a population of 309 (as of the 2006
census). It is located on St. Mary's Bay and can be accessed via Route 100 or
Route 92. Nearby communities include Point Lance and St. Bride's, Newfoundland
and Labrador.
